<lyrics>[V1]
 1- qạlwly ʿlyh bysạmḥ wqạlwly ʿlyh qlbh kbyr
 qạlwạ bynsy̱ klạmy ạljạrḥ mn gẖyr lwm wlạ tfkyr
 lqyt qlby yạybny wrạyḥ nạḥyẗ qlbh wmsẖtạq lyh
 wf lylh mn ạlyạly lfyt nwrh jạly
 bdly kl ḥạly dqt bjd ạlạ̉mạn
 dh bnẓrh ʿynh jạbny sẖạl ʿny ạlly tạʿbny
 wqạly ạ̹nh ḥạbbny wsẖạryny mn zmạn
 2- rby msẖ bs bysạmḥ dh byskb skyb ạlrwḥ
 hw gẖfrly kẖṭạyạ ạ̹mbạrḥ wrwḥh mʿạyạ mnyn mạbrwḥ
 wlạ̉nh byʿml ly ạlṣạlḥ sạyb trtyb bkrh lyh
 ạlly gẖfrly kẖṭạyạ ạmbạrḥ ạ̉nạ hạrmy kl ḥmwly ʿlyh
 ạnạ kẖwfy f lḥẓẗ sạbny mn ywm mạ bạ̹ydh sẖạlny
 f sạʿthạ ḥbh ạ̉srny ʿwḍwny ʿn ạlly rạḥ
 mdylh snyny ạljạyẗ wlạ ạ̉ḍyʿ fyhạ tẖạnyẗ
 wkmạn hạkẖdmh bʿnyạ dh ạlly f ḥḍnh bạrtạḥ</lyrics>
<title>skyb ạlrwḥ</title>
